description: Main entry point for a Vue.js front-end application, setting up the app with plugins and mounting it to the DOM.

methods.name: createApp
methods.description: Creates a new Vue application instance with the root component App.

methods.name: createPinia
methods.description: Creates a new Pinia store instance for state management.

methods.name: app.use
methods.description: Registers plugins or other Vue features with the application.

methods.name: app.mount
methods.description: Mounts the Vue application onto the DOM element with id 'app'.
